J_n(y):=\int\cosh^{2n}y\ dy\ .
\eqalign{J_n(y)&=\int\cosh^{2n-1}y\ \cosh y\ dy\cr &= \cosh^{2n-1}y\ \sinh y - (2n-1)\int \cosh^{2n-2}y\ \sinh^2 y\ dy \cr &= \cosh^{2n-1}y\ \sinh y - (2n-1)\int \cosh^{2n-2}y\ (\cosh^2 y-1)\ dy\cr &=\cosh^{2n-1}y\ \sinh y -(2n-1)\bigl(J_n(y)-J_{n-1}(y)\bigr)\ .\cr }
